  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_3d00e7b28dad67d6e49e6f07a128fc11">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Banners, pennants, pillows, runners, jackets, blazers, reunion items, graduation robes and regalia and other cloth items including a Cornell University doctoral hood, originally owned by Dr. William J. Edens, Ph.D.      1937 and Class of 1941 blazer owned by Arthur Townsend Klinger.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_3aaaf302cf110cdb3e1f2b6f5bdbd102">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Class of 1941 blazer owned by Arthur Townsend Klinger 1941.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_100ae9a67b5badb52356253c23e7ec9c">
